	<digest>Rolling mean and standard deviation on list inputs</digest>
	<description><div class="document">
<p>Computes the rolling mean and sample standard deviation over a given window for multichannel list inputs.</p>
</div>
</description>
  <discussion>
      <h4><openfilelink filename="Fluid Corpus Manipulation Toolkit.maxpat">Open the Overview Patch</openfilelink></h4>
    <div class="document">
<p>Each element of the list is dealt with in parallel. This is particularly suitable for multidimensional descriptors.</p>
</div>


		fluid.stats is part of the Fluid Decomposition Toolkit of the FluCoMa project. For more explanations, learning material, and discussions on its musicianly uses, visit <a href="http://www.flucoma.org/">flucoma.org</a>.

